  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help the old man to reach the top of the mountain. Solve the puzzles to progress. No time limit no stress just relax and think. Who knows there might be suprises.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is a slow paced puzzle game where the objective of the game is to flip tiles to reveal a diorama. Can you find the hidden stars?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Flip tiles to solve the puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cozy environments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Minigames</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievments</p></li></ul>",
